      "comment": "MY LADY ASH (7) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten 1.5 lengths (23.85) behind Great North at this track. Likely to feature again. LILLY MOIRA (1) finds it hard to break through. Finished in the minors latest when second (23.70) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Can measure up. MISS GRAHAM (2) was below best at her last start when 8th at Gosford following a third place finish (23.74) at this track two back. Key runner on best form. GARIN (8) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
